  <brief_title>Adherence, Efficacy and Safety of an Insulin Protocol in the Critically Ill: A Prospective Observational Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adherence, Efficacy and Safety of an Insulin Protocol in the Critically Ill: A Prospective Observational Study</official_title>
